headline: W.W. Grainger (GWW): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: W.W. Grainger trades at $914.93 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, losing 11.1% over the last six months while the S&P 500 is down 13.8%. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
